Lightning Point is an Australian television teen drama set in the modern day with fantasy elements .
It was filmed on location at the Gold Coast in 2011 .
The half-hour series is produced by Jonathan M. Shiff for Network Ten in association with Nickelodeon and German public broadcaster ZDF .
It was re-broadcast on Network Ten in Australia on 22 June 2012 , and again on the same network from 5 July 2014 .
The series premiered on TeenNick in the United States under its international title of Alien Surf Girls on 29 May 2012 , and aired on Nickelodeon in the United Kingdom from 23 July 2012 also as Alien Surf Girls .
It was announced by co-star Jessica Green that the series will not return for a second season .